bermaid2019.htm|title=The Chambermaid (2019)|website=[[Box Office Mojo]]|accessdate=8 November 2019}}</ref><ref name=\"NUM\">{{cite web|url=https://www.the-numbers.com/movie/Camarista-La-(Mexico)-(2019)#tab=summary|title=The Chambermaid (2019)|website=[[The Numbers (website)|The Numbers]]|accessdate=8 November 2019}}</ref>\n}}\n'''''The Chambermaid''''' ({{lang-es|'''La camarista'''}}) is a 2018 Mexican [[drama film]] directed by [[Lila Avil\u00e9s]]. It was selected as the Mexican entry for the [[Academy Award for Best International Feature Film|Best International Feature Film]] at the [[92nd Academy Awards]], but it was not nominated.<ref name=\"Mexico\">{{cite web|url=https://www.eluniversal.com.mx/espectaculos/cine/mexico-apuesta-por-la-camarista-para-los-oscar |title=M\u00e9xico apuesta por ''La camarista'' para los Oscar y los Goya |work=eluniversal |accessdate=12 September 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/oscars-mexico-selects-chambermaid-international-feature-category-1239240 |title=Oscars: Mexico Selects 'The Chambermaid' for International Feature Category |work=The Hollywood Reporter |first=John |last=Hecht |accessdate=12 September 2019}}</ref>\n\n==Plot==\nWorking at an upscale Mexican hotel, a maid seeks to find her place in the world.<ref name=\"Observor\">{{cite web|url=https://observer.com/2019/06/the-chambermaid-la-camarista-review-gabriela-cartol/ |last=Jones |first=Oliver |title=Gabriela Cartol Brings \u2018The Chambermaid\u2019 to Life With Bristling Sensitivity and Dormant Rage |work=[[The New York Observer]] |date=22 June 2019 |accessdate=12 September 2019}}</ref>\n\n==Cast==\n* [[Gabriela Cartol]]\n* [[Agustina Quinci]]\n* [[Teresa S\u00e1nchez]]\n\n==Reception==\n''The Chambermaid'' holds an 81/100 average on [[Metacritic]].<ref>{{Citation|title=The Chambermaid|url=https://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-chambermaid|access-date=2019-10-09}}</ref>\n\n==See also==\n* [[List of submissions to the 92nd Academy Aw